metadata.name: Communal Taxi
metadata.description:
Havana, Cuba, 2014

Street photography by Gulnara Samoilova. 

Gulnara is a street and fine art photographer, author and founder of Women Street Photographers. She received national and international awards, including first prize in the World Press Photo competition. Gulnara's  work is a part of major collections such as the Museum of the City of New York, The New York Public Library, New York Historical Society, Houston Museum of Fine Arts, and in the private collections such as of Sir Elton John.
